animeDescription: Official music video for Scenarioart's How Low Sympathy a part of their 1st mini Album titled night walking.This is "Queen" and "Spot" story.Queen is the sun. Spot is the universe.Queen is energy. Spot is source.Queen is power. Spot is a moment and eternity, ALL.Queen noticed. She was perfect all. All the time.Presence, anxiety, conflict. Body feel the emotion.Joy of the queen is "I remember all".(Source: Official site)
